# Smart Packing - Full Stack Project Structure

## Project Overview
This is a full-stack application with a React Native frontend (Expo) and Express.js backend. The project supports Android, iOS, and Web platforms with a robust backend API.

## Key Files and Directories

### Root Configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root project configuration with workspace management
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project documentation

### Frontend (React Native + Expo)
- [frontend/](mdc:frontend/) - React Native application directory
  - [frontend/package.json](mdc:frontend/package.json) - Frontend dependencies and scripts
  - [frontend/app.json](mdc:frontend/app.json) - Expo configuration with platform-specific settings
  - [frontend/tsconfig.json](mdc:frontend/tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration for frontend
  - [frontend/eslint.config.js](mdc:frontend/eslint.config.js) - ESLint configuration for frontend
  - [frontend/app/](mdc:frontend/app/) - Main application directory using Expo Router
  - [frontend/components/](mdc:frontend/components/) - Reusable React components
  - [frontend/constants/](mdc:frontend/constants/) - Frontend constants and theme
  - [frontend/hooks/](mdc:frontend/hooks/) - Custom React hooks
  - [frontend/assets/](mdc:frontend/assets/) - Static assets

### Backend (Express.js + TypeScript)
- [backend/](mdc:backend/) - Express.js backend application
  - [backend/package.json](mdc:backend/package.json) - Backend dependencies and scripts
  - [backend/tsconfig.json](mdc:backend/tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration for backend
  - [backend/.eslintrc.js](mdc:backend/.eslintrc.js) - ESLint configuration for backend
  - [backend/src/](mdc:backend/src/) - Backend source code
    - [backend/src/index.ts](mdc:backend/src/index.ts) - Main server entry point
  - [backend/env.example](mdc:backend/env.example) - Environment variables template

## Platform Support
- **Frontend**: React Native with Expo (Android, iOS, Web)
- **Backend**: Express.js API server (Node.js)

## Key Technologies
### Frontend
- React Native 0.79.5
- Expo SDK 53
- TypeScript for type safety
- Expo Router for navigation
- React Navigation for tab navigation

### Backend
- Express.js 4.18.2
- TypeScript for type safety
- Node.js runtime
- CORS, Helmet, Morgan for security and logging
- Rate limiting and compression middleware

## Development Workflow
- Use `npm run dev` to start both frontend and backend
- Use `npm run dev:frontend` for frontend only
- Use `npm run dev:backend` for backend only
- Use `npm run build` to build both applications
- Use `npm run lint` to lint both frontend and backend
